1 tin Pineapple Slices
1 packet chicken breast strips
½ lemon
2 sprig spring onion
1 bag baby spinach leaves
1 bag slaw mix
6 Mini Flour Tortillas
1 packet Mango Mayonnaise
1 sachet Mild Caribbean Jerk Seasoning
olive oil

• Drain and chop pineapple
• In a bowl, combine seasoning, chicken and a drizzle of olive oil
• Heat oil in frying pan over high heat
• Cook chicken and pineapple, tossing, until cooked through, 3-4 mins.

• Cut lemon into wedges. Slice spring onion
• Roughly chop spinach
• In a second bowl, combine slaw mix, spring onion, spinach and a squeeze of lemon juice
• Add a drizzle of oil, season and toss.

• Microwave tortillas for 10 secondbursts, until warm
• Chop chicken
• Spread mango mayo over tortillas
• Fill tortillas with slaw, chicken and pineapple
• Serve with remaining lemon wedges